Package: assurance
Type: Package
Title: Assurance for Clinical Trial Design 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jeremy E. Oakley
Maintainer: Jeremy Oakley <j.oakley@sheffield.ac.uk>
Description: Estimates assurance (probability of a successful outcome) of a randomised controlled trial with two arms and normally distributed data,given elicited prior distributions for the treatment effect and observation variances.
